## ğŸ§  Part 3: Deployment via Docker Compose & Auto-Update (40 points)

### ğŸ“ Folder Structure on VM

A folder `todo-app-deploy` was created on the VM containing:

* `docker-compose.yml`
* `.env`

ğŸ“¸ **Folder Structure on VM:**
![vm-folder](screenshots/vm-folder.png)

### ğŸ§¾ docker-compose.yml

```yaml
version: "3.8"
services:
  todo-app:
    image: olarashad/todo-node-app:latest
    ports:
      - "4000:4000"
    env_file:
      - .env
    healthcheck:
      test: ["CMD", "curl", "-f", "http://localhost:4000"]
      interval: 30s
      timeout: 10s
      retries: 3

  watchtower:
    image: containrrr/watchtower
    volumes:
      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock
    command: --interval 30
```

